          "number": 1,
          "slidetitle": "Insecure AI API Integrations",
          "subtitle": "Risks of connecting apps to AI",
          "slidecontent": "• Apps increasingly rely on external AI services to add smart features\n• These connections introduce new security risks many developers overlook\n• Sensitive data can leak through poorly configured API calls\n• Attackers can manipulate inputs to hijack AI behaviour\n• Real consequences include data breaches, compliance failures, and reputational damage",
